The paper discusses reasoning over semantically annotated data in stream processing, which is a topic related to databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of a scalable RDF stream processing engine also suggests a focus on distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the evaluation of the system along different dimensions and over multiple datasets indicates a potential focus on data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
